statements: SELECT * FROM biometric_authentication;
SELECT biometric_id, authentication_status FROM biometric_authentication WHERE authentication_status = true;
SELECT * FROM biometric_authentication WHERE biometric_id = 100;
SELECT biometric_id, biometric_data FROM biometric_authentication WHERE authentication_status = false;

SELECT * FROM biometric_data;
SELECT biometric_type, biometric_feature FROM biometric_data;
